\begin_layout Standard
Colors and fonts of certain elements of classicthesis can be tweaked by
 redefining some internal commands: 
\family typewriter

\backslash
ct@altfont
\family default
 and 
\family typewriter

\backslash
ct@caps
\family default
 are hooks to alter the basic look of everything that uses spaced caps.
 For example, for 
\family typewriter
arsclassica
\family default
 we used 
\family typewriter

\backslash
renewcommand*{
\backslash
ct@altfont}{
\backslash
sffamily}
\family default
.
 Coloring is also possible this way.
 Check the corresponding commands in 
\family typewriter
classicthesis.sty
\family default
 for further ideas and implementation details.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Several color names have been introduced to easily change chapter number,
 title or hyperreference colors: 
\family typewriter
CTsemi
\family default
 will affect the color used for chapter numbers, the default is 
\family typewriter

\backslash
definecolor{CTsemi}{gray}{0.55}
\family default
; 
\family typewriter
CTtitle
\family default
 can be used to change the title color from the default crimson red 
\family typewriter

\backslash
definecolor{CTtitle}{named}{Maroon}
\family default
, and so on.
 Color settings are handled by 
\family typewriter
xcolor
\family default
 package, check the documentation for other named colors (in the dvipsnames
 set) and other possibilities.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Many other customisations in 
\family typewriter
classicthesis-config.tex
\family default
 are possible, but you should be careful with making changes there, since
 some changes could cause errors.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Note Comment
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Finally, if really needed, changes can be made in the file 
\family typewriter
classic\SpecialChar softhyphen
thesis.sty
\family default
,
\begin_inset Marginal
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Modifications in 
\family typewriter
classicthesis.sty
\end_layout

\end_inset

 although this is mostly not designed for user customisation.
 Some commands from 
\family typewriter
classicthesis.sty
\family default
 can be repeated at the end of 
\family typewriter
classicthesis-config.tex
\family default
 to change the default behavior — the text-block size can be adjusted, for
 example, to get longer lines of text.
 
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

