\begin_layout Standard
We chose (and currently stick with) the 
\size footnotesize
GPL
\size default
 because we would not like to compete with proprietary modified versions
 of our own work.
 However, the whole template is free as free beer and free as free speech.
 We will not demand the sources for theses, books, CVs, etc.
 that were created using classicthesis.
\end_layout

